Enum ConstraintForm

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ConstraintForm>
      • com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.mrcm.ConstraintForm
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ConstraintForm>, org.eclipse.emf.common.util.Enumerator

    public enum ConstraintForm
extends java.lang.Enum<ConstraintForm>
implements org.eclipse.emf.common.util.Enumerator
    A representation of the literals of the enumeration 'Constraint Form', and utility methods for working with them. Indicates the model or post-coordinated form to which a constraint applies.
    See Also:
    MrcmPackage.getConstraintForm()
